                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300114-49-off276 t18300114-49-cd277"></join>, 1 pair of trousers, value 30s.; 1 waistcoat, value 10s.; 1 razor, value 1s.; 1 handkerchief, value 4s.; 1 pin, value 4s., and 1 pair of gloves, value 1s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18300114-49-victim443" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Strachan
